name: Canopy Portal into Violet Falls
description: Violet Falls is located at the Easterly South edge of Gyre Island which is growing at the time of this minting. Violet Falls do not have an IRL analog but the canopy portal does. This Canopy Portal grants buyer one extra unsold objkt issued by gyreisland_xtz after purchase of this Master objkt. What's behind Violet Falls remains a mystery but perhaps the extra objkt may offer clues.
